        <Meaning id="212db107-4f3f-4b69-ba0e-bbb9b7fc20d8" type="Adjective">
          <Vi>nguyên tố; hàng đầu, tốt nhất</Vi>
          <En>1. (mathematics) having no positive divisors other than 1 and itself; 2. being the best or most important of its kind</En>
          <Example>7 is a prime number; She is the prime candidate for the job.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="9ebeabe3-830e-4f15-a874-a533ce1d5323">
